Homework 02 - Jobs to be done

" Play golf anywhere and anytime "

Functional job
 - Minimize cost of course and caddy fee every time golfer play
 - Minimize cost from buying updated golf equipments
 - Maximize number of golf course that golfer can go
 - Maximize number of place that golfer can play

Emotional job
 - Minimize time it takes to go to golf course 
 - Minimize waiting time when there are too much golfers in golf course
 - Minimize likelihood of skin getting dark from sunlight

Social Job
 - Minimize likelihood of getting accident during golf round
 - Maximize number of players that always limited
